cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY 

This paper focuses on real-time recognition using deep neural networks on IoT devices, specifically for image and video recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of parallelism and distributed computing, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Additionally, the paper proposes a dynamic and adaptive approach to utilizing IoT devices, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper evaluates the energy consumption and performance of their system, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
